OL,3,CBonnie Tyler: From south Wales pubs to
OL,4,Cone of music's most enduring voices
OL,6,FITV News' Mahatir Pasha looks back on
OL,7,Fthe life of the 80s icon
OL,9,FShe was the instantly recognisable,
OL,10,Fraspy-voiced rock singer whose iconic
OL,11,Fhits have stayed popular across
OL,12,Fgenerations.
OL,14,FBorn as Gaynor Hopkins in 1951, Bonnie
OL,15,FTyler - as she would later become
OL,16,Fknown - grew up in a working-class
OL,17,Ffamily in a small village near Swansea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
