OL,3,CBonnie Tyler: From south Wales pubs to
OL,4,Cone of music's most enduring voices
OL,6,FAfter seven years performing in pubs
OL,7,Fand clubs around South Wales, her big
OL,8,Fbreak came when she was spotted by a
OL,9,Ftalent scout.
OL,11,FHer first major hit, Lost in France,
OL,12,Fwas released in 1976. But it would be
OL,13,Fher mega hit Total Eclipse of the
OL,14,FHeart that propelled her to
OL,15,Finternational stardom, topping music
OL,16,Fcharts for weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
