OL,3,CBonnie Tyler: From south Wales pubs to
OL,4,Cone of music's most enduring voices
OL,6,FDecades later, in anticipation of the
OL,7,Ftotal solar eclipse of August 2017 -
OL,8,Fduring which she performed her most
OL,9,Ficonic song live on a cruise ship -
OL,10,Fthe hit became the number one
OL,11,Fdownloaded in America.
OL,13,FAnd earlier this year, 43 years after
OL,14,Fits initial release, the chart-topper
OL,15,Fcemented its place as one of the most
OL,16,Ffamous power ballads of all time by
OL,17,Fsurpassing a billion streams on
OL,18,FSpotify.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
