OL,3,CBonnie Tyler: From south Wales pubs to
OL,4,Cone of music's most enduring voices
OL,6,FTyler also represented the UK at the
OL,7,FEurovision Song Contest in 2013 and
OL,8,Fwas made an MBE for her services to
OL,9,Fmusic in 2023.
OL,11,FNo one could deny the blonde-haired
OL,12,F80s queen's presence - having spent
OL,13,Fover 50 years in the music industry.
OL,15,FIn May, Tyler was placed into an
OL,16,Finduced coma following emergency
OL,17,Fsurgery in Portugal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
