OL,3,CBonnie Tyler: From south Wales pubs to
OL,4,Cone of music's most enduring voices
OL,6,FThe following month, her team posted a
OL,7,Fstatement to say that Tyler was no
OL,8,Flonger in a coma, but remained "very
OL,9,Funwell and in intensive care in
OL,10,Fhospital in Portugal."
OL,12,FOn July 9, Tyler passed away
OL,13,Funexpectedly as a result of the
OL,14,Fillness that she was being treated for.
OL,16,FEven at the age of 75, Tyler had gigs
OL,17,Flined up across Europe from later on
OL,18,Fthis month.
OL,20,FShe had been scheduled to perform in
OL,21,FGermany on July 10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
